{"tid":1669310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】7.21元朗白衣人恐襲 66.3%受訪者認為涉「警黑合作」","createTime":"2019-10-22T13:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T15:09:20.000Z","uid":27451,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"00dc582ad86834cf498b2a0c98f0d80a697581ca","tid":1669310,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:04:40.000Z","msg":"【抗暴之戰】7.21元朗白衣人恐襲 66.3%受訪者認為涉「警黑合作」<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191022&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60182422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191022%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60182422&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=0606e92e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191022%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60182422&h=48c75a3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191022&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60182422</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係掛，得66.3咁少？"},{"pid":"c61888e818954cd4a1f3d7df100fc4b3b33f924b","tid":1669310,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係呀,我知我地講近廢話,但前線的確需要支援</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n有班住係平衡時空分分鐘連發生過都唔知"},{"pid":"83e241586bd3f5a24e59fa05312b16e110228531","tid":1669310,"uid":284304,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:06:37.000Z","msg":"點解咁少...係咪係元朗訪問"},{"pid":"d5ef6518497af39dfc014368f412ececa5f86058","tid":1669310,"uid":267914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:06:50.000Z","msg":"其實比數好大，你計返20-30係藍絲"},{"pid":"768d1b0e079ab41211ae9f3b362b264999bbf9ef","tid":1669310,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"7.21元朗白衣人無差別襲擊事發至今，警方只僅僅檢控數名施襲者，加上當日儼如「無警時份」的安排，令人質疑「警黑合作」。香港民意研究今日啟動名為「我們香港人」的民調計劃，據其發表的首次調查結果，多達66.3%人受訪者認為7.21元朗恐襲中警方與黑社會合作，另有66.2%受訪者相信有公安或武警混入香港警察。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【抗暴之戰】警親屬3歲童校內疑被多次拍打心口 將軍澳幼師被控虐兒<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究今日開始啟動名為「我們香港人」的滾動調查計劃，讓市民提出希望進行民調的題目，若一條問題獲1萬人要求進行民調研究便會被採納，研究所同時開始為計劃眾籌，目標是800萬元，使計劃至少運作至今年底。<br />\n<br />\n有份發起計劃的梁啟智稱，民調一般由付費者主導，這可說是某種權力，而今次計劃就是將民調的問題開放給公眾，讓公眾充權。研究主席及行政總裁鍾庭耀亦稱，計劃是因應有意見反映，自反送中後社會變得分化，甚至反修例一方也會有不同看法，故是為了解民意而設立此機制。"},{"pid":"faa149c50f26566a442c3a28cee74eebcd6f99f9","tid":1669310,"uid":69916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:07:34.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"86bb0414d5a48644cd055fa5b2a3289cbc69eb33","tid":1669310,"uid":27451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"83e241586bd3f5a24e59fa05312b16e110228531","tid":1669310,"uid":284304,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:06:37.000Z","msg":"點解咁少...係咪係元朗訪問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"其餘果d咪係黑警家人黑社會家人同班弱智藍屍囉"},{"pid":"4fc33b02b42ed99ea2f36e0d589a5b462d9bf73d","tid":1669310,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:10:19.000Z","msg":"剩低33.7%係咪覺得警=黑"},{"pid":"a939e49e67a396e38dc7862ee2adda3778262318","tid":1669310,"uid":27451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d5ef6518497af39dfc014368f412ececa5f86058","tid":1669310,"uid":267914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:06:50.000Z","msg":"其實比數好大，你計返20-30係藍絲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得起碼80%先合理，盲都睇得出係警黑合作啦"},{"pid":"6cc8bc8e9aecc139687475abd6ab330e8b478f05","tid":1669310